---
// WhyBookUs.astro — Why Book T-MAC UK? section for the Book Us page
// Requirement 9.7: at least 3 value propositions as styled cards with icons
---

<section class="py-16 bg-cream">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-navy text-center mb-12">
      Why Book T-MAC UK?
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

      <!-- Authentic African Sound -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 flex flex-col items-start">
        <div class="mb-4 text-gold">
          <!-- Music note SVG icon -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M9 3v10.55A4 4 0 1 0 11 17V7h4V3H9zm-2 16a2 2 0 1 1 0-4 2 2 0 0 1 0 4z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-navy mb-3">Authentic African Sound</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Experience the genuine rhythms and harmonies of African choral music, performed by
          singers deeply rooted in their cultural heritage.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Versatile Repertoire -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 flex flex-col items-start">
        <div class="mb-4 text-gold">
          <!-- Globe/world SVG icon -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 17.93c-3.95-.49-7-3.85-7-7.93 0-.62.08-1.21.21-1.79L9 15v1c0 1.1.9 2 2 2v1.93zm6.9-2.54c-.26-.81-1-1.39-1.9-1.39h-1v-3c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H8v-2h2c.55 0 1-.45 1-1V7h2c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-.41c2.93 1.19 5 4.06 5 7.41 0 2.08-.8 3.97-2.1 5.39z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-navy mb-3">Versatile Repertoire</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          From traditional folk songs to contemporary gospel and highlife, our diverse repertoire
          suits weddings, corporate events, festivals, and community gatherings.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Professional Excellence -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 flex flex-col items-start">
        <div class="mb-4 text-gold">
          <!-- Star SVG icon -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-navy mb-3">Professional Excellence</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          With over a decade of performance experience, T-MAC UK delivers polished, memorable
          performances that leave lasting impressions on audiences of all sizes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Community Impact -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 flex flex-col items-start">
        <div class="mb-4 text-gold">
          <!-- Handshake/people SVG icon -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5C6.34 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.97 1.97 3.45V19h6v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-navy mb-3">Community Impact</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Every booking supports our community outreach programmes, helping us bring the joy of
          African music to schools, care homes, and community centres across the Midlands.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
